reviews.text: The taste of food is good, but not soup.
The food is amazing! Came all the way from Shenzhen to try out the food because of a recommendation. Did not disappoint!

It's a pretty legitimate local experience, with very local servers and ambience. They even open up the tables onto the streets at night, when the inside area gets too crowded. That's probably as local Hong Kong as you can get! Food is also pretty legitimate for the price paid.
Terrible service. we left, and ate elsewhere

reviews.text: 油麻地區内－家擁有50多年歴史的燒味飯店，燒鵝馳名其他亦具水準，菜紅腸(内有灼生菜鲜鵝腸豬紅)也非常滋味，值得－試！
油麻地隱世燒臘飯店，此處出品的廣東燒味味道出色 ! 價錢適中，實為果欄地區燒臘店的必然選擇！
一般平民式燒臘飯店，無装修，無好招呼，但求一個快速進食還可以。
一個星都不給，甚麼都唔掂，一定冇下次 👎
現在由創店老闆經營番，燒鵝回復水準嘞
